# Portfolio (ICS4U)

## About Me
Hi, I’m Alexander Liliang. I’m a Grade 12 student taking ICS4U.
I enjoy model games and I like building small interactive projects.

## Skills & Tools
- HTML / CSS / JavaScript
- Basic programming logic (variables, loops, functions)
- Git & GitHub
